    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスライブの準備もこれで一段落か\nにしても、ララさん達が来てから事務所に物が増えたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3893177137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あれもこれも……ララさんの発明品というやつだろうか\nなんでオフィスにあるのかは分からないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hit-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3219.4333395000003,
          "startTime": 19.7194333395
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fall-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3119.4332839000012,
          "startTime": 19.6194332839
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "きゃああっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6194332839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんだ？　後ろから凄い音が！？\nというか今の声、聞き覚えが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2386780716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "振り返っちゃダメーー！\n{user}さん、そのまま動かないで！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9560997964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なんで振り返っちゃダメなんだ……？\nその声、瑠依だよな？　無事なのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3894324383,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_transform-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14024.4679054,
          "startTime": 47.4139003437
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "いいからお願いします！　えっと、何か着るものは……\nあら、何かしらこのバッジ……きゃっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8128140383,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3767.752972000004,
          "startTime": 48.5805670103
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依がいきなり事務所に現れた？）\n（一体何が起こっているんだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2728617471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "これヤミさんの……す、すみません、お待たせしました\nえっと、ここ、事務所……ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6472344716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだけど……なぜヤミさんの服を着てるんだ？\nそれに、どこから事務所に入って来たんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2000055949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私にもよく分からないんですけど、ララさんに発明品を\n見せてもらっていたら、いつの間にかここにいたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9449488957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、なぜか、服が、その……あの……\nと、とにかく、騒がしくしてしまってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6782822291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "この服は、ララさんの発明品の機能だと思います\n散らばっていたものに触れたら、気付いたら着ていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0372090973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これがなかったら大変なことになっていました\nうぅ……最近、こんなトラブルばかりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3449458439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それは大変だったな……でも「これがなかったら」って\n……え？　瑠依、まさか、さっきまで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.4333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違います！　服だけ残してワープして来たとか\nそんなこと一切ありませんから！　全然違いますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9245334625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かった分かった、もう追及しない。……ところで\n寮にも事務所にもララさんの発明品が沢山あるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1333435059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。元々、発明品は寮にだけあったはずなんですけど\nすみれやこころが事務所に持ち込んだみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8104975065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人ったら、面白がってあれこれ借りて遊んで……\n何も知らない人が不用意に触ったら、危ないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3438308399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、事務所は外部の人の出入りもあるし\n遊ぶのはいいけど、寮に持ち帰ってもらわないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "では、いい機会ですし、私が持ち帰ります\nレッスンスタジオにもあったと思うので、見てきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.800044187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "助かるよ、ありがとう\nオフィスにある分は俺が集めるから、そっちは頼んだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.966671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.3061401766
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.3061401766
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.5561401766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……集め終わったけど、だいぶ量が多いな\nやっぱり俺も、瑠依と一緒に寮まで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.3333384197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.1792526326
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "きゃああっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.1792526326,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5091.455133700009,
          "startTime": 194.2707077663
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6787.419120400017,
          "startTime": 195.966671753
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.4792628052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_13_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "また瑠依の悲鳴！？　瑠依、大丈夫か？\nおーい！　入るからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.0518814624,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6847.368441100002,
          "startTime": 200.8992499035
        },
        {
